#: ../../user_docs/magic_word.md:1
msgid "Magic Word"
msgstr "幻词"

#: ../../user_docs/magic_word.md:2
msgid "Magic Words are some characters that have special meanings. They will be evaluated to some pre-defined characters. For one simple example, date could be evaluated to the date of today."
msgstr "幻词是一些具有特殊含义的字符。它们将被识别为一些预先定义好的字符。举一个简单的例子，date可以识别为今天的日期。"

#: ../../user_docs/magic_word.md:4
msgid "VNote support snippets in most of the input widgets. For example, you could use snippet for the note name when creating a note."
msgstr "VNote在大多数输入窗口小部件中支持片段插入。例如，您可以在创建备注时插入片段作为备注名称。"

#: ../../user_docs/magic_word.md:6
msgid "%da% work log.md will be evaluated as 20180128 work log.md since %da% is a magic word which is defined as the date of today in the form YYYYMMDD."
msgstr "%da% work log.md将识别为20180128 work log.md ，因为%da%是一个幻词，它以YYYYMMDD的形式定义为今天的日期。"

#: ../../user_docs/magic_word.md:8
msgid "In the editor, you could type %da%, and then press shortcut Ctrl+E M, which will evaluate the word under cursor as magic word."
msgstr "在编辑器中，您可以键入 %da%，然后按快捷键 Ctrl+E M，它将光标下的单词识别为幻词。"

